"{\"uid\": \"jamaicaobserver.com-2024-08-10-olympics-chief-thomas-bach-says-will-not-seek-third-term\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"PARIS,\\u00a0France (AFP) - International Olympic Committee (IOC) President Thomas Bach said at the Paris Games on Saturday he will not seek to remain in charge for a third term.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 172, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"New times are calling for new leaders,\\\" the 70-year-old German lawyer, who has been in charge since 2013, told a session of IOC members in the French capital.\", \"from\": 174, \"to\": 333, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 231, \"end\": 237, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/German_language\", \"score\": 0.7099782990914713, \"rank\": 0.40679666910148876, \"text\": \"German\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/German_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/German_language\"}, {\"begin\": 299, \"end\": 302, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 0.999999999981128, \"rank\": 1.4562244805253285e-11, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 318, \"end\": 324, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9604703824657579, \"rank\": 0.03682295090460432, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Bach said he was asked to stay in his role but insisted he would not attempt to extend his mandate by changing the Olympic charter that limits the president to a maximum of 12 years in the role.\", \"from\": 335, \"to\": 529, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 335, \"end\": 339, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johann_Sebastian_Bach\", \"score\": 0.9999920480206705, \"rank\": 7.952042527506088e-06, \"text\": \"Bach\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johann_Sebastian_Bach\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johann_Sebastian_Bach\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I know with this decision I am disappointing many of you\\u2026but it is in the best interests of our beloved Olympic movement,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 531, \"to\": 663, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"His successor will be elected in 2025.\", \"from\": 665, \"to\": 703, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The jostling to succeed Bach will now begin, with some well-informed IOC watchers tipping Zimbabwean former swimmer Kirsty Coventry for the role.\", \"from\": 705, \"to\": 850, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 729, \"end\": 733, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johann_Sebastian_Bach\", \"score\": 0.9999920480206705, \"rank\": 7.952042527506088e-06, \"text\": \"Bach\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johann_Sebastian_Bach\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johann_Sebastian_Bach\"}, {\"begin\": 774, \"end\": 777, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 0.999999999981128, \"rank\": 1.4562244805253285e-11, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 821, \"end\": 836, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kirsty_Coventry\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kirsty Coventry\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kirsty_Coventry\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kirsty_Coventry\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tags:  HOUSE RULES\", \"from\": 852, \"to\": 870, \"entities\": []}]}"